snippet.title: Bolt Bot Screwy Viruses Trailer
snippet.description:

Take control of a robot named Bolt in over 50 levels of 3D platforming fun inspired by 90's and early 2000's classic platform games. It is a collect-a-thon at heart and rewards the player constantly in an evolving hub world!
